haskell-conduit-extra: haskell-conduit-extra (adapters for common libraries)
haskell-conduit-extra:
haskell-conduit-extra: The conduit package itself maintains relative small dependencies. The
haskell-conduit-extra: purpose of this package is to collect commonly used utility
haskell-conduit-extra: functions wrapping other library dependencies, without depending
haskell-conduit-extra: on heavier-weight dependencies. The basic idea is that this package
haskell-conduit-extra: should only depend on haskell-platform packages and conduit.
